I"N<h3 id="29190923--mac快捷键光标及-delete-删除光标右侧文字">29190923:  【Mac快捷键】光标及 delete 删除光标右侧文字</h3>
<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Ctrl</code> + <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">a</code> = home
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Ctrl</code> + <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">e</code> = end
